the sin of harold diddlebock is a 1947 comedy film written and directed by preston sturges , starring the silent film comic icon harold lloyd , and featuring an incredible supporting cast including jimmy conlin , raymond walburn , rudy vallee , arline judge , edgar kennedy , franklin pangborn , j. farrell macdonald , robert dudley , robert greig , lionel stander and especially , jackie the lion .

lloydering : this silent screen comedian came out of retirement to act in a 1947 film " the sin of harold diddlebock "

harold lloyd